        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1717130445" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8886231485414664892">This is one of the finest books I have ever read. I don&apos;t collect books, but I want this book in my personal library.<br/><br/>The book is fascinating because many of the essays he wrote about civil rights and race in America were written while the issues and events he wrote about were actually occurring. Sadly much of what he described is still topical today. <br/><br/>The book also contains reviews of films, books, and plays.<br/><br/>Many of the pieces would be emotionally burdensome and hard to read in the hands of anyon</span>
  <span id="freeText8886231485414664892" style="display:none">This is one of the finest books I have ever read. I don't collect books, but I want this book in my personal library.<br /><br />The book is fascinating because many of the essays he wrote about civil rights and race in America were written while the issues and events he wrote about were actually occurring. Sadly much of what he described is still topical today. <br /><br />The book also contains reviews of films, books, and plays.<br /><br />Many of the pieces would be emotionally burdensome and hard to read in the hands of anyone else. Baldwin's prose has clarity, wit, and heart. I did laugh, and I did cry.</span>
  <a data-text-id="8886231485414664892" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
