        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer257805283" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11650853743058571056">This is not something that you can rush through. I have been reading it on and off for two months. Each essay takes a good deal of time and thought to process and reflect upon. Although his topics are not in my particular areas of expertise or study, I found many things in them to enjoy and contemplate. </span>

