              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/2582612-bananya?shelf=most-loved-of-all-time">most-loved-of-all-time</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1445861290" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13469570831644624304">REPLACING MY COPY stat...EVEN MORE RELEVANT TODAY. Jimmy was perfection...</span>

